message.content:
Great to hear that you're interested in investing in crypto! To help you better, I need to understand your financial situation and goals. Here are a couple of questions:

1. What is your investment experience? Are you a beginner, intermediate, or advanced investor?
2. What is your risk tolerance? Are you looking for high-risk, high-reward opportunities, or do you prefer more stable investments?

Your answers will help me tailor my advice to your needs!
